==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: chéng xiān qĭ hòu
===Etymology===
Short for: [[承继|承<font color="gray">继</font>]][[先人|先<font color="gray">人</font>]][[的|<font color="gray">的</font>]][[遗教|<font color="gray">遗教</font>]]，[[并|<font color="gray">并</font>]][[开启|<font color="gray">开</font>启]][[后来|后<font color="gray">来</font>]][[的|<font color="gray">的</font>]][[事业|<font color="gray">事业</font>]][http://140.111.34.46/cgi-bin/dict/GetContent.cgi?Database=dict&DocNum=116713&GraphicWord=yes&QueryString=承先启后] (inherit the teachings of previous generations in order to inspire future actions).

===Idiom===
# carry on the past heritage and open up the future; serve as a link between past and future.

